snippet.title: State of Emergency Trailer
snippet.description: State of Emergency is a "man against the mob" arcade-like fighting game where you are a member of an underground resistance movement, dedicated to liberating your people from the oppressive Corporation.Use hand to hand combat, weapons, and anything you can find on the street.Hundreds of people are rioting as you fight for freedom - be careful!
